Note: ============================================================
Note: HIR_ARRAY_TYPE post handler (13006)
Note: ============================================================

@Reasoning
HIR_ARRAY_TYPE post: array type [T] or fixed-size array. The
element type has been visited as child 0. The array layout
(element size, count) is consumed by alloca lowering and
indexed-access lowering.
@End Reasoning

@Implementation
Returns 1.
@End Implementation

@Performance_Hints
Zero cost beyond the dispatch trampoline.
@End Performance_Hints

@Security_Scope
No state mutation.
@End Security_Scope

