Note: ============================================================
Note: HIR_TYPE_PARAMETER post handler (13009)
Note: ============================================================

@Reasoning
HIR_TYPE_PARAMETER post: a generic type parameter (e.g., the T
in List[T]). Resolved to a concrete type at instantiation time
by monomorphization. The handler is a marker; monomorphization
will use this hook in v0.0.9.x.
@End Reasoning

@Implementation
Returns 1.
@End Implementation

@Performance_Hints
Zero cost beyond the dispatch trampoline.
@End Performance_Hints

@Security_Scope
No state mutation.
@End Security_Scope

