Note: ============================================================
Note: HIR_REFERENCE_TYPE post handler (13011)
Note: ============================================================

@Reasoning
HIR_REFERENCE_TYPE post: reference type (&T or &mut T). Inner
type is visited as a child. Reference types lower to pointer
values at the MIR layer; the handler itself is a metadata
marker.
@End Reasoning

@Implementation
Returns 1.
@End Implementation

@Performance_Hints
Zero cost beyond the dispatch trampoline.
@End Performance_Hints

@Security_Scope
No state mutation.
