Note: ============================================================
Note: HIR_SLICE_TYPE post handler (13013)
Note: ============================================================

@Reasoning
HIR_SLICE_TYPE post: slice type [T] — a view into a contiguous
array. Inner element type is visited. Slice representation is a
fat pointer (ptr + length); the metadata is used by indexed-
access lowering.
@End Reasoning

@Implementation
Returns 1.
@End Implementation

@Performance_Hints
Zero cost beyond the dispatch trampoline.
@End Performance_Hints

@Security_Scope
No state mutation.
@End Security_Scope

