    Return 1
End Process

Note: ============================================================
Note: Type Handler Registration
Note: ============================================================

@Reasoning
Installs every HIR type-node handler in the lowering dispatch
table. All 15 type handlers are post-only (no children traversal
work needed at the lowering layer — children are walked by the
visitor framework and their results are consumed by parent
expression/declaration handlers).
@End Reasoning

@Implementation
Sequence of lowering_register_handler calls covering 13000-13014.
Each registers a post-only handler; pre/child_enter/child_exit
slots are 0.
@End Implementation

@Performance_Hints
Cold path, called once per lowering pass.
@End Performance_Hints

@Security_Scope
Validates table non-null.
@End Security_Scope

